title: Pictures Of OK Jaanu Screening: Aditya, Shraddha, Sidharth, Alia & Others Watch The Film
text: tweet The special screening of upcoming romantic musical drama OK Jaanu was held last night in Mumbai. Apart from the film’s cast Aditya Roy Kapur, Shraddha Kapoor and Naseeruddin Shah and producer Karan Johar, Bollywood young brigades – Ranveer Singh, Sidharth Malhotra, Varun Dhawan, Alia Bhatt, Sushant Singh Rajput, Kriti Sanon and others attended this screening. Check out their pictures right here: Aditya Roy Kapur during the screening of OK Jaanu Shraddha Kapoor during the screening of OK Jaanu Varun Dhawan during the screening of OK Jaanu Sidharth Malhotra during the screening of OK Jaanu Alia Bhatt during the screening of OK Jaanu Aditya Roy Kapur and Shraddha Kapoor during the screening of OK Jaanu Sushant Singh Rajput during the screening of OK Jaanu Kriti Sanon during the screening of OK Jaanu Sooraj Pancholi during the screening of OK Jaanu Siddhanth Kapoor during the screening of OK Jaanu Rhea Chakraborty during the screening of OK Jaanu Ranveer Singh during the screening of OK Jaanu Swara Bhaskar during the screening of OK Jaanu Karan Johar during the screening of OK Jaanu Sophie Choudhary during the screening of OK Jaanu Malaika Arora Khan during the screening of OK Jaanu Bhushan Kumar and Divya Khosla Kumar during the screening of OK Jaanu Naseeruddin Shah and Ratna Pathak during the screening of OK Jaanu SHARE
